To
The undersigned is directed to inform Members of the
Council of Ministers that Shri Manharlal Mansukhlal Shah
assumed office as Minister with effect from today, the 1st May,
1956 (forenoon). He will be designated as Minister of
Industrial Development and function in the Ministry of Commerce
& Industry.
No. 75/CF/52.
GOVERNMENT OF INDIA
CABINET SECRETARIAT
New Delhi, the 1st May, 1956.
M: 69
All Members of the Council of Ministers.
KHÔNG ĐƯỜNG THUẬT ĐƯỢC MONG
